Note on the encyclical text

The encyclical *Magnifica Humanitas* (Pope Leo XIV, 15 May 2026) is
© Libreria Editrice Vaticana. Excerpts reproduced in this repository
(notably in `skills/magnifica-humanitas/references/encyclical-excerpts.md`)
are used under fair-use principles for the purpose of moral discernment
in technical work, with citation to chapter and section. The full
authoritative text is available at:

  https://www.vatican.va/content/leo-xiv/en/encyclicals/documents/20260515-magnifica-humanitas.html

If you redistribute or adapt this repository, please preserve those
citations and the link to the source.
